  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this research is to study the effect of a loading dose of colchicine on the
      occurrence of periprocedural myocardial infarction (PPMI) in elective percutaneous coronary
      intervention.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
